\fs28 Week 1 \'96 Crazy People, Crazy Prayers\

\fs30 \
Intro:\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sb100\sa100\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl0
\f1\b0\fs28 \cf2 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}New series and stuff\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}God\'92s power > Our reality  \
\pard\pardeftab720\sb100\sa100\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sb100\sa100\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f0\b \cf3 Transition:  The problem is though for most of us here we already know that don\'92t we?\
\pard\pardeftab720\sb100\sa100\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

